<text><body>
<cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">三　長老之譬喻二</cb:mulu><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">第二十二　哈提品</cb:mulu><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">二二〇　巴巴尼瓦利耶（抑惡）</cb:mulu><ref target="#PTS.Ap.213" type="PTS_hide"></ref><cb:div type="other">
<pb ed="N" xml:id="N29.0017.0309a" n="0309a"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0309a01"/><milestone unit="juan" n="23"/><cb:mulu type="卷" n="23"></cb:mulu>
<lb ed="N" n="0309a02"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">第二十三　阿蘭巴那達耶迦品</cb:mulu><head>第二十三　阿蘭巴那達耶迦品</head>
<lb ed="N" n="0309a03"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0309a04"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0309a05"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">二二一　阿蘭巴那達耶迦（支撑物布施）</cb:mulu><head>二二一　阿蘭巴那達耶迦（支撑物布施）</head>
<lb ed="N" n="0309a06"/><p xml:id="pN29p0309a0601">一</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0309a0601" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">阿塔達西佛，如是彼世尊，世間居上首，吾施支撑物。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0309a07"/><p xml:id="pN29p0309a0701">二</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0309a0701" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">海空盡廣闊，行進此地上，生而為王者，亦為大地王。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0309a08"/><p xml:id="pN29p0309a0801">三</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0309a0801" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">燃盡眾煩惱，除去諸有結，通達於三明，興作佛教<anchor xml:id="beg_a" type="cb-app"/>已<anchor xml:id="end_a"/>。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0309a09"/><p xml:id="pN29p0309a0901">四</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0309a0901" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">六十二劫昔，大力有三王，其名稱一見<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0309001" n="0309001"/>，出為轉輪王。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0309a10"/><p xml:id="pN29p0309a1001">五</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0309a1001" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">四種無礙解……</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0309a11"/><p xml:id="pN29p0309a1101" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">——如是尊者阿蘭巴那達耶迦長老宣唱此等偈。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="N" n="0309a12"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0309a13"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0309a14"/>
<pb ed="N" xml:id="N29.0017.0310a" n="0310a"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0310a01"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0310a02"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0310a03"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">二二二　阿吉那達耶迦（裘布施）</cb:mulu><head>二二二　阿吉那達耶迦（裘布施）</head>
<lb ed="N" n="0310a04"/><p xml:id="pN29p0310a0401">一</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0310a0401" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">三十劫往昔，吾為作蓆工，吾見離垢佛，以受尊供物。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0310a05"/><p xml:id="pN29p0310a0501">二</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0310a0501" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">世統尸棄佛，吾施碎皮片，吾由於此業，兩足人中尊。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0310a06"/><p xml:id="pN29p0310a0601"><ref target="#PTS.Ap.214"></ref>三</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0310a0601" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">吾享無顧樂，燃盡眾煩惱，等正覺者教，吾保最後身。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0310a07"/><p xml:id="pN29p0310a0701">四</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0310a0701" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">吾施此皮衣，三十一劫間，惡趣吾不知，施皮衣果報。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0310a08"/><p xml:id="pN29p0310a0801">五</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0310a0801" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">第五劫往昔，有王名善施<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0310001" n="0310001"/>，大力具七寶，出為轉輪王。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0310a09"/><p xml:id="pN29p0310a0901">六</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0310a0901" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">四種無礙解……</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0310a10"/><p xml:id="pN29p0310a1001" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">——如是尊者阿吉那達耶迦長老宣唱此等偈。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="N" n="0310a11"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0310a12"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0310a13"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0310a14"/>
<pb ed="N" xml:id="N29.0017.0311a" n="0311a"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0311a01"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0311a02"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">二二三　多衛羅達尼耶（二寶）</cb:mulu><head>二二三　多衛羅達尼耶（二寶）</head>
<lb ed="N" n="0311a03"/><p xml:id="pN29p0311a0301">一</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0311a0301" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">吾昔為獵人，棲居於森林，得見離垢佛，受吾尊供物。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0311a04"/><p xml:id="pN29p0311a0401">二</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0311a0401" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">毘婆尸大仙，吾施以肉片，人天諸世界，吾為王統治。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0311a05"/><p xml:id="pN29p0311a0501">三</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0311a0501" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">由肉片布施，於吾生二寶，此世有二寶，為此世利益。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0311a06"/><p xml:id="pN29p0311a0601">四</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0311a0601" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">吾享此等果，肉片利益故，吾以身體柔，頭腦運思細。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0311a07"/><p xml:id="pN29p0311a0701">五</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0311a0701" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">爾時吾施肉，九十一劫間，惡趣吾不知，肉施此果報。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0311a08"/><p xml:id="pN29p0311a0801">六</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0311a0801" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">第四劫往昔，其名稱大赤<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0311001" n="0311001"/>，大力一人王，出為轉輪王。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0311a09"/><p xml:id="pN29p0311a0901">七</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0311a0901" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">四種無礙解……</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0311a10"/><p xml:id="pN29p0311a1001" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">——如是尊者多衛羅達尼耶長老宣唱此等偈。</p>
<lb ed="N" n="0311a11"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0311a12"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0311a13"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0311a14"/><p xml:id="pN29p0311a1401" rend="margin-left:22em">——第十誦品——</p></cb:div>
<pb ed="N" xml:id="N29.0017.0312a" n="0312a"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0312a01"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0312a02"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0312a03"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">二二四　阿拉迦達耶迦（守護布施）</cb:mulu><head>二二四　阿拉迦達耶迦（守護布施）</head>
<lb ed="N" n="0312a04"/><p xml:id="pN29p0312a0401">一</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0312a0401" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">悉達多佛陀，吾為作欄楯，善逝彼大仙，行施以守護。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0312a05"/><p xml:id="pN29p0312a0501">二</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0312a0501" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">因吾業之著，恐怖戰慄無，無論生何處，吾更無所懼。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0312a06"/><p xml:id="pN29p0312a0601"><ref target="#PTS.Ap.215"></ref>三</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0312a0601" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">為作欄楯故，九十四劫間，惡趣吾不知，布施欄楯果。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0312a07"/><p xml:id="pN29p0312a0701">四</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0312a0701" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">第六劫往昔，稱名為倚依<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0312001" n="0312001"/>，大力具七寶，出為轉輪王。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0312a08"/><p xml:id="pN29p0312a0801">五</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0312a0801" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">四種無礙解……</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0312a09"/><p xml:id="pN29p0312a0901" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">——如是尊者阿拉迦達耶迦長老宣唱此等偈。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="N" n="0312a10"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0312a11"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0312a12"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0312a13"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">二二五　阿烏耶底迦（無病）</cb:mulu><head>二二五　阿烏耶底迦（無病）</head>
<lb ed="N" n="0312a14"/><p xml:id="pN29p0312a1401">一</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0312a1401" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">於毘婆尸佛，吾施與火室，是病患所居，溫水隨意取。</l></lg>
<pb ed="N" xml:id="N29.0017.0313a" n="0313a"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0313a01"/><p xml:id="pN29p0313a0101">二</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0313a0101" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">行此善業故，得身體健美，吾不知疾病，福業之報果。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0313a02"/><p xml:id="pN29p0313a0201">三</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0313a0201" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">吾施彼之室，九十一劫間，惡趣吾不知，布施火室果。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0313a03"/><p xml:id="pN29p0313a0301">四</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0313a0301" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">第七劫往昔，有王名無敗<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0313001" n="0313001"/>，大力具七寶，出為轉輪王。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0313a04"/><p xml:id="pN29p0313a0401">五</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0313a0401" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">四種無礙解……</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0313a05"/><p xml:id="pN29p0313a0501" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">——如是尊者阿烏耶底迦長老宣唱此等偈。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="N" n="0313a06"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0313a07"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0313a08"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0313a09"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0313a10"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">二二六　羌庫拉普毘耶（羌庫拉花）</cb:mulu><head>二二六　羌庫拉普毘耶（羌庫拉花）<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0313001-1" n="0313001-1"/></head>
<lb ed="N" n="0313a11"/><p xml:id="pN29p0313a1101">一</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0313a1101" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">吾名那羅陀，姓為迦葉波，見第一沙門，天敬毘婆尸。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0313a12"/><p xml:id="pN29p0313a1201">二</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0313a1201" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">彼受尊供物，具諸好佛陀，吾採羌庫拉<anchor xml:id="beg_b" type="cb-app"/><space quantity="0"/><anchor xml:id="end_b"/>，奉獻彼佛陀。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0313a13"/><p xml:id="pN29p0313a1301">三</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0313a1301" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">供養鮮花故，九十一劫間，惡趣吾不知，供佛此果報。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0313a14"/><p xml:id="pN29p0313a1401">四</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0313a1401" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">七十四劫昔，有王羅瑪莎，華鬘所裝飾，壯牛為拖車。</l></lg>
<pb ed="N" xml:id="N29.0017.0314a" n="0314a"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0314a01"/><p xml:id="pN29p0314a0101"><ref target="#PTS.Ap.216"></ref>五</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0314a0101" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">四種無礙解……</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0314a02"/><p xml:id="pN29p0314a0201" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">——如是尊者羌庫拉普毘耶長老宣唱此等偈。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="N" n="0314a03"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0314a04"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0314a05"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0314a06"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0314a07"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">二二七　瓦單薩奇耶（頭飾）</cb:mulu><head>二二七　瓦單薩奇耶（頭飾）</head>
<lb ed="N" n="0314a08"/><p xml:id="pN29p0314a0801">一</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0314a0801" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">吾由苑中出，往見世導師，造作黃金色，手持貴頭飾。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0314a09"/><p xml:id="pN29p0314a0901">二</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0314a0901" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">疾速由彼處，即登象背行，捧與世緣者，毘婆尸佛陀。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0314a10"/><p xml:id="pN29p0314a1001">三</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0314a1001" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">供養此鮮花，三十一劫間，惡趣吾不知，供佛此果報。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0314a11"/><p xml:id="pN29p0314a1101">四</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0314a1101" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">二十七劫昔，出世一人王，名謂大光輝<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0314001" n="0314001"/>，大力轉輪王。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0314a12"/><p xml:id="pN29p0314a1201">五</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0314a1201" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">四種無礙解……</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0314a13"/><p xml:id="pN29p0314a1301" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">——如是尊者瓦單薩奇耶長老宣唱此等偈。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="N" n="0314a14"/>
<pb ed="N" xml:id="N29.0017.0315a" n="0315a"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0315a01"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0315a02"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0315a03"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0315a04"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0315a05"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">二二八　明奢瓦單薩奇耶（核頭飾）</cb:mulu><head>二二八　明奢瓦單薩奇耶（核頭飾）</head>
<lb ed="N" n="0315a06"/><p xml:id="pN29p0315a0601">一</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0315a0601" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">言說尸棄佛，救主涅槃時，吾撒眾頭飾，供養菩提樹。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0315a07"/><p xml:id="pN29p0315a0701">二</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0315a0701" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">其時供養故，三十一劫間，惡趣吾不知，供養此果報。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0315a08"/><p xml:id="pN29p0315a0801">三</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0315a0801" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">二十六劫昔，其名稱雲聚<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0315001" n="0315001"/>，大力具七寶，出為轉輪王。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0315a09"/><p xml:id="pN29p0315a0901">四</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0315a0901" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">四種無礙解……</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0315a10"/><p xml:id="pN29p0315a1001" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">——如是尊者明奢瓦單薩奇耶長老宣唱此等偈。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="N" n="0315a11"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0315a12"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0315a13"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0315a14"/>
<pb ed="N" xml:id="N29.0017.0316a" n="0316a"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0316a01"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0316a02"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">二二九　須伽陀威利耶（巧作華鬘）</cb:mulu><head><ref target="#PTS.Ap.217"></ref>二二九　須伽陀威利耶（巧作華鬘）</head>
<lb ed="N" n="0316a03"/><p xml:id="pN29p0316a0301">一</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0316a0301" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">吾名阿私陀，時作華鬘人，手持香華鬘，行往捧獻王。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0316a04"/><p xml:id="pN29p0316a0401">二</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0316a0401" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">尚未至王前，吾見尸棄佛，內心喜雀躍，即此捧獻佛。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0316a05"/><p xml:id="pN29p0316a0501">三</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0316a0501" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">供養此花故，三十一劫間，惡趣吾不知，供佛此果報。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0316a06"/><p xml:id="pN29p0316a0601">四</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0316a0601" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">二十五劫昔，有大威力王，大力名二荷<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0316001" n="0316001"/>，出為轉輪王。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0316a07"/><p xml:id="pN29p0316a0701">五</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0316a0701" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">四種無礙解……</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0316a08"/><p xml:id="pN29p0316a0801" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">——如是尊者須伽陀威利耶長老宣唱此等偈。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="N" n="0316a09"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0316a10"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0316a11"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0316a12"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0316a13"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">二三〇　耶迦萬第耶（一禮）</cb:mulu><head>二三〇　耶迦萬第耶（一禮）</head>
<lb ed="N" n="0316a14"/><p xml:id="pN29p0316a1401">一</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0316a1401" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">莊嚴大雄者，毘舍浮佛陀，吾喜心清淨，禮拜殊勝佛。</l></lg>
<pb ed="N" xml:id="N29.0017.0317a" n="0317a"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0317a01"/><p xml:id="pN29p0317a0101">二</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0317a0101" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">彼時行此業，三十一劫間，惡趣吾不知，拜佛此果報。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0317a02"/><p xml:id="pN29p0317a0201">三</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0317a0201" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">二十四劫昔，名喚離歡喜<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0317001" n="0317001"/>，大力具七寶，出為轉輪王。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0317a03"/><p xml:id="pN29p0317a0301">四</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0317a0301" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">四種無礙解……</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0317a04"/><p xml:id="pN29p0317a0401" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">——如是尊者耶迦萬第耶長老宣唱此等偈。</p>
<lb ed="N" n="0317a05"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0317a06"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0317a07"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0317a08"/><p xml:id="pN29p0317a0801" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">攝頌：</p>
<lb ed="N" n="0317a09"/><lg xml:id="lgN29p0317a0901" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:3em">阿蘭巴那、阿吉那、曼薩達與阿拉伽達耶迦</l>
<lb ed="N" n="0317a10"/><l rend="text-indent:3em">阿烏耶底羌庫拉、孫那<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0317001-1" n="0317001-1"/>、明奢瓦單薩</l>
<lb ed="N" n="0317a11"/><l rend="text-indent:3em">須伽陀威利耶、耶迦萬第耶，十人共偈五十五。</l></lg></cb:div></cb:div>
<lb ed="N" n="0317a12"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0317a13"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0317a14"/>
</cb:div></body>
